race.comment: RED FEATHER BOA (12) finished runner-up over this track and trip last time out and is another to draw favourably in gate two. Include in calculations. PLATINUM GIFT (11) strips fitter third-up from the break and may earn some minor money. QUEST OF QUESTS (7) has been readied for the return with a solid trial and owns a good record at this distance so keep safe. RED TOFFEE (9) best of the rest.
